%20in%20the%20initial%2048%20hours.%20However%2C%20it%20was%20followed%20by%20more%20than%2020%2C000%20cyber%20attacks%2C%20including%201%2C340%20attempts%20to%20steal%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fover-20000-attempts-to-hack-crowd-funding-site-in-past-2-days-claims-congress-2820090%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20they%20had%20anticipated%20these%20attacks%20and%20implemented%20robust%20firewalls%20to%20tackle%20this%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20breakdown%20of%20the%20payment%20preferences%20of%20donors%20showed%20that%2081%25%20chose%20the%20UPI%20route%2C%20followed%20by%20credit%20cards%20(7.95%25)%2C%20debit%20cards%20(6.34%25)%2C%20net%20banking%20(4.78%25)%2C%20and%20a%20minimal%200.02%25%20opting%20for%20RTGS-NEFT.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20enhance%20the%20donation%20drive%2C%20Congress%20treasurer%20Ajay%20Maken%20has%20outlined%20a%20three-pronged%20strategy%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20includes%20sending%20observers%20to%20states%20for%20leader%20training%20ahead%20of%20the%20door-to-door%20campaign%20starting%20on%20December%2028.%20QR%20codes%20will%20be%20displayed%20at%20Congress%20rallies%20to%20facilitate%20donations%2C%20and%20the%20party%20is%20exploring%20the%20possibility%20of%20raising%20funds%20through%20merchandising%2C%20featuring%20items%20like%20T-shirts%20signed%20by%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20financial%20aspect%2C%20the%20donation%20drive%20serves%20as%20a%20means%20for%20the%20party%20to%20connect%20with%20its%20supporters.%20Data%20collected%20through%20the%20campaign%20will%20be%20shared%20with%20state%20units%2C%20enabling%20targeted%20outreach%20efforts%20to%20strengthen%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20ties%20with%20its%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703143679000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-says-fundraisin