0Escobar%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20wasn't%20aware%20that%20he%20was%20a%20drug%20lord.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DX4edQHCIais%26ab_channel%3Ddjvlad%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVladTV%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%2056-year-old%20rapper%20revealed%20that%20he%20hung%20out%20with%20the%20Colombian%20drug%20lord%20and%20the%20Cocaine%20Cowboys%20%26quot%3Bmany%2C%20many%20times%26quot%3B%20in%20Miami%20because%20they%20%26quot%3Bwere%20all%20friends.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20would%20land%20helicopters%20in%20my%20house%20constantly%20on%20Star%20Island%2C%20come%20into%20my%20house%2C%26quot%3B%20Vanilla%20Ice%20told%20VladTV.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20food%20just%20for%20them%20in%20the%20refrigerators.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rapper%20added%20that%20they%20would%20also%20fly%20him%20about%20in%20their%20helicopters%20and%20race%20boats%20together.%20Beyond%20going%20to%20events%20and%20racing%20with%20Escobar%20and%20his%20crew%2C%20Vanilla%20Ice%20said%20he%20did%20know%20who%20they%20were%20and%20%26quot%3Bnever%20questioned.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20didn't%20have%20Google.%20I%20don't%20know%20who%20these%20people%20are.%20I%20thought%20they%20were%20businessmen%2C%26quot%3B%20Vanilla%20Ice%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20what%20the%20drug%20kingpin%20was%20like%20in%20real%20life%2C%20the%20rapper%20described%20him%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bgreat%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20acknowledged%20that%20he%20sounded%20ridiculous%20for%20saying%20that.%20He%20added%20that%20it%20was%20not%20common%20practice%20to%20ask%20people%20what%20they%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirst%20of%20all%2C%20like%2C%20I%20had%20no%20Google.%20You%20don't%20go%20up%20to%20people%20and%20go%2C%20'What%20do%20you%20do%20for%20a%20living%3F'%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20no%20idea%2C%20bro.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20separate%20interview%20with%20%3Ca