-ice-friends-with-pablo-escobar-colombian-drug-lord-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20separate%20interview%20with%20TMZ%2C%20the%20rapper%20said%20he%20only%20realized%20something%20was%20off%20when%20he%20was%20questioned%20by%20the%20FBI.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22agoh%40businessinsider.com%20(Amanda%20Goh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Top%20bowler%2C%20but...'%3A%20Gillespie%20questions%20Cummins'%20IPL%20price%20tag%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703142956000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106176016%2Cimgsize-31834.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fipl%2Ftop-stories%2Fpat-is-a-top-quality-bowler-but-jason-gillespie-questions-pat-cummins-ipl-price-tag%2Farticleshow%2F106175509.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Australian%20fast%20bowler%20Jason%20Gillespie%20has%20raised%20doubts%20about%20Pat%20Cummins'%20high%20price%20tag%20in%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL).%20Gillespie%20believes%20that%20T20%20cricket%20is%20not%20Cummins'%20strongest%20format%2C%20but%20supports%20Mitchell%20Starc's%20record-breaking%20deal.%20Cummins%2C%20the%20Australian%20captain%2C%20was%20involved%20in%20a%20bidding%20war%20for%20a%20contract%20worth%20Rs%2020.50%20crore.%20Gillespie%20believes%20that%20while%20Cummins%20is%20a%20top-quality%20bowler%20and%20great%20leader%2C%20he%20excels%20in%20Test%20cricket%2C%20which%20is%20where%20he%20excels.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22At%207-Month%20Low%2C%20Job%20Creation%20in%20Formal%20Sector%20Declined%20by%2016.7%25%20in%20October%3A%20EPFO%20Data%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F28134446%2F3891925784_eb02c9d8e3_o.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3ESignalling%20a%20downturn%20in%20the%20labour%20market%2C%20fresh%20formal%20employment%20creation%20in%20October%20declined%20by%2016.7%25%20in%20comparison%20to%20September.%20While%20the%20number%20of%20jobs%20created%20in%20September%20stood%20at%209%2C26%2C%20934%2C%20the%20number%20reduced%20to%207%2C72%2C084%20in%20October%2C%20according%20to%20the%20latest%20payroll%20data%20released%20by%20the%20Employees%E2%80%99%20Provident%20Fund%20Organisation%20(EPFO).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EPFO%20payroll%20data%20helps%20to%20track%20employment%20creation%20in%20the%20formal%20sector%2C%20as%20every%20new%20employee%20must%20sign%20up%20for%20a%20provident%20fund%20under%20the%20EPFO.%20The%20National%20Statistical%20Office%20(NSO)%20too%20uses%20the%20EPFO%20data%20to%20analyse%20employment%20trends%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%2068.7%25%20(5%2C30%2C884)%20of%20the%20total%207%2C72%2C084%20who%20joined%20the%20workforce%20in%20October%20were%20in%20the%20age%20group%20of%2018-28%20age%2C%20accounting%20for%20the%20highest%20among%20new%20EPF%20subscribers%20in%20October.%20The%20same%20figure%20had%20stood%20at%2068.5%25%20in%20the%20previous%20month%20of%20September%2C%20%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Standard%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Ffresh-formal-job-creation-dips-to-7-month-low-in-october-shows-epfo-data-123122001097_1.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0quoting%20official%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20those%20who%20joined%20the%20workforce%20and%20registered%20themselves%20as%20new%20EPF%20subscribers%20in%20the%20age%20group%20above%2035%20reduced%20from%2016.1%25%20in%20September%20to%2015.9%25%20in%20October.%20Women%E2%80%99s%20share%2C%20however%2C%20saw%20a%20marginal%20increase%20from%2025.2%25%20in%20September%20to%2026.4%25%20in%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20net%20payroll%20addition%20increased%20by%201%25%2C%20taking%20the%20number%20from%201.51%20million%20in%20September%20to%201.53%20million%20in%20October.%20The%20net%20payroll%20figure%20is%20worked%20out%20by%20taking%20into%20account%20the%20number%20of%20new%20subscribers%2C%20the%20number%20of%20exits%2C%20and%20the%20return%20of%20old%20subscribers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20released%20by%20the%20Centre%20for%20Monitoring%20Indian%20Economy%20(CMIE)%20for%20the%20months%20under%20consideration%20also%20indicated%20the%20rise%20in%20the%20unemployment%20rate.%20According%20to%20CMIE%E2%80%99s%20Consumer%20Pyramids%20Household%20Survey%2C%20it%20shot%20from%207.09%25%20in%20September%20to%2010.09%25%20in%20October.%20The%20rise%20in%20joblessness%20was%20attributed%20to%20a%20sharp%20jump%20in%20the%20rural%20unemployment%20rate%20to%2010.82%25%20from%206.2%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703142932000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F28134446%2F3891925784_eb02c9d8e3_o.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fat-7-month-low-job-creation-in-formal-sector-declined-by-16-7-in-october-epfo-data%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20number%20of%20new%20jobs%20created%20in%20the%20formal%20sector%20came%20down%20to%207%2C72%2C084%20in%20October%20from%209%2C26%2C%20934%20in%20September.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fat-7-month-low-job-creation-in-formal-sector-declined-by-16-7-in-october-epfo-data%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Think%20your%20bank's%20interest%20rates%20are%20bad%3F%20Just%20take%20a%20look%20at%20Japan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Customers%20at%20the%20Japanese%20banking%20corporation%20ATM%20machines%20of%20MUFG%20and%20Mizuho%20banks%20seen%20in%20Tokyo.%5C%22