%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKushagra%2C%20an%20uncapped%20Indian%20with%20a%20base%20price%20of%20Rs%2020%20lakh%2C%20had%20left%20a%20lasting%20impression%20on%20Ganguly%20who%20was%20reminded%20of%20MS%20Dhoni%20seeing%20the%20young%20lad%20play.%20But%2C%20Shashikant%20felt%20his%20son%20might%20only%20go%20for%20his%20base%20price%20despite%20Dada's%20promise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20thought%20he%20will%20get%20picked%20by%20Capitals%20at%20base%20price.%20For%20a%20few%20minutes%2C%20I%20was%20so%20numb.%20One%20can%20only%20think%20about%20miracles%2C%20and%20today%20was%20that%20kind%20of%20day.%20He%20was%20confident%20because%20Ganguly%20had%20promised%20him%2C%20but%20I%20thought%20he%20must%20have%20said%20this%20to%20encourage%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Shashikant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20never%20played%20cricket%20at%20any%20level.%20I%20was%20just%20a%20keen%20follower.%20When%20he%20was%20five%20and%20started%20showing%20interest%20in%20cricket%2C%20I%20decided%20that%20I%20would%20coach%20him.%20A%20colleague%20suggested%20a%20book%20named%20Art%20and%20Science%20of%20Cricket%20by%20Bob%20Woolmer.%20I%20must%20have%20read%20that%20book%20at%20least%20four%20or%20five%20times.%20That%20book%20became%20my%20coach%20and%20I%20started%20training%20Kushagra%2C%26quot%3Bhe%20recalled.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703135460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F3cbr48a8_ganguly_625x300_20_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fsourav-ganguly-promised-dc-would-bid-till-rs-10-crore-father-of-uncapped-star-whos-bit-of-ms-dhoni-4708960%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kumar%20Kushagra%20was%20bought%20for%20Rs.%207.2%20crore%20by%20Delhi%20Capitals%20in%20IPL%202024%20auction.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fsourav-ganguly-promised-dc-would-bid-till-rs-10-crore-father-of-uncapped-