%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Ftwitter-review-vicky-kaushal-is-being-hailed-as-the-scene-stealer-in-dunki%2Farticleshow%2F106170388.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BSomebody%20Will%20Have%20To%20Pay...%26quot%3B%3A%20Gambhir%20On%20Starc's%20Rs%2024.75%20Crore%20IPL%20Bid%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20mentor%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20has%20justified%20his%20franchise%20bidding%20for%20Mitchell%20Starc%20for%20a%20record-breaking%20amount%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20Australia%20quick%20will%20be%20the%20X-factor%20and%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20bowling%20pack.%20KKR%20shelled%20out%20a%20jaw-dropping%20Rs%2024.75%20crore%20to%20get%20the%20services%20of%20Starc%20in%20the%20IPL%20auction%20in%20Dubai%20on%20Tuesday.%20%26quot%3BHe%20(Starc)%20is%20an%20X-factor%2C%20there%20is%20no%20doubt%20about%20that.%20Someone%20who%20can%20bowl%20with%20the%20new%20ball%2C%20bowl%20in%20the%20death%20overs%20and%20more%20importantly%2C%20someone%20who%20can%20lead%20the%20attack%2C%26quot%3B%20Gambhir%2C%20who%20was%20present%20at%20the%20auction%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20is%20going%20to%20be%20of%20massive%20help%20to%20our%20two%20domestic%20bowlers%20because%20both%20of%20them%20are%20very%20talented%20and%20you%20need%20someone%20to%20help%20them%20out%20in%20the%20middle%20and%20Starc%20covers%20those%20bases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20only%20about%20his%20bowling%20but%20also%20about%20leading%20the%20attack%20and%20helping%20all%20guys%20around%20him.%20So%2C%20somebody%20will%20have%20to%20pay%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20India%20opener%20told%20Jio%20Cinema.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGambhir%2C%20who%20captained%20KKR%20to%20two%20IPL%20titles%2C%20said%20for%20him%20having%20a%20strong%20bowling%20line-up%20takes%20precedence%20over%20a%20strong%20batting%20line-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20depth%20in%20our%20bowling%20line-up.%20We%20always%20wanted%20to%20have%20a%20stronger%20bowling%20attack%20and%20now%20we%20have%20the%20options%20with%20Mujeeb%20(Ur%20Rahman)%2C%20Gus%20(Atkinson)%2C%20Sunil%20(Narine)%2C%20Varun%20(Chakravarthy)%2C%20and%20Mitchell%20Starc%20along%20with%20two%20Indian%20seamers%20(Harshit%20Rana%20and%20Suyash%20Sharma)%20and%20Chetan%20Sakariya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20we%20have%20enough%20options%20where%20we%20can%20play%20different%20combinations%20looking%20at%20the%20venue%20as%20well.%20For%20me%2C%20it%20has%20always%20been%20about%20having%20a%20strong%20bowling%20line-up%20compared%20to%20a%20very%20strong%20batting%20line-up%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20BJP%20Member%20of%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20his%20coming%20back%20to%20the%20franchise%20he%20had%20led%20to%20titles%20in%202012%20and%202014%2C%20Gambhir%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFor%20me%2C%20KKR%20is%20not%20a%20team%2C%20it%20is%20an%20emotion.%20The%20reason%20is%20the%20amount%20of%20love%20that%20I%20have%20received%20from%20the%20people%20of%20Kolkata%20for%20seven%20years%20that%20I%20led%20them%20and%2C%20hopefully%2C%20I%20led%20them%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20honesty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHopefully%2C%20we%20can%20recreate%20the%20same%20memories%20that%20we%20did%20in%202012%20and%202014.%20There%20is%20no%20guarantee%20that%20we%20will%20go%20out%20and%20win%20but%20there%20is%20one%20guarantee%20for%20sure%2C%20that%20we%20will%20fight%20till%20the%20last%20drop%20of%20our%20blood.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703132400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fgette5bo_mitchell-starc-icc_625x300_17_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fsomebody-will-have-to-pay-gautam-gambhir-on-mitchell-starcs-rs-24-75-crore-ipl-2024-auction-bid-4709509%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gautam%20Gambhir%20has%20justified%20his%20franchise%20bidding%20for%20M