20high%20accuracy%20in%20forecasting%20individuals'%20lifespans.%20Modeled%20after%20ChatGPT%2C%20the%20AI%20Life2vec%20system%20utilizes%20personal%20information%20like%20health%2C%20education%2C%20occupation%2C%20and%20income%20for%20its%20predictions.%20Drawing%20on%20Denmark's%20population%20data%2C%20the%20model%20refines%20its%20accuracy.%20Analyzing%20health%20and%20labor%20market%20data%20from%202008%20to%202020%20involving%206%20million%20people%2C%20the%20death%20predictor%20achieves%20a%2078%20percent%20accuracy%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20use%20the%20technology%20behind%20ChatGPT%20(something%20called%20transformer%20models)%20to%20analyze%20human%20lives%20by%20representing%20each%20person%20as%20the%20sequence%20of%20events%20that%20happen%20in%20their%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Sune%20Lehmann%2C%20lead%20author%20of%20the%20December%202023%20study%20%26quot%3BUsing%20sequence%20of%20life%20events%20to%20predict%20human%20lives%2C%26quot%3B%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2023%2F12%2F20%2Ftech%2Fai-death-calculator-predicts-when-youll-die-its-extremely-accurate%2F%3Futm_source%3Dwhatsapp%26utm_campaign%3Dandroid_nyp%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20New%20York%20Post.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20use%20the%20fact%20that%2C%20in%20a%20certain%20sense%2C%20human%20lives%20share%20a%20similarity%20with%20language%2C%26quot%3B%20explained%20Mr%20Lehmann.%20%26quot%3BJust%20like%20words%20follow%20each%20other%20in%20sentences%2C%20events%20follow%20each%20other%20in%20human%20lives.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMortality%20prediction%20is%20an%20often-used%20task%20within%20statistical%20modeling%20that%20is%20closely%20related%20to%20other%20health%20prediction%20tasks%20and%20therefore%20requires%20life2vec%20to%20model%20the%20progression%20of%20individual%20health%20sequences%20as%20well%20as%20labor%20history%20to%20predict%20the%20correct%20outcome%20successfully%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20authors%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs43588-023-00573-5.epdf%3Fsharing_token%3DkXXhmleEuWfp3GiA4gqkmtRgN0jAjWel9jnR3ZoTv0MCA8ZigxRuse4dwzhHzdeU_N0IihJNSnkNn8IuSOiDqAQb47Y-8uupmV9QjDCAu6AOGJARzak-dwM7p4X9TQQ9LcijQEALh6hk2ivQPtTrTxhwEwUiqzKsHTaAWVskhehTCmeunFI92psfwokEX55GxsmzrWSx8QHwkLjxyQTViBSnzlwewQB8a2_Xeykp2uU%253D%26tracking_referrer%3Dwww.dailymail.co.uk%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Estudy%20wrote.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20ChatGPT%2C%20which%20focuses%20on%20crafting%20creative%20text%20or%20navigating%20professional%20hurdles%2C%20Life2vec%20takes%20a%20different%20approach.%20This%20AI%20delves%20into%20the%20personal%20histories%20of%20individuals%2C%20analyzing%20details%20like%20health%2C%20education%2C%20career%2C%20and%20income.%20Through%20this%20deep%20examination%2C%20Life2vec%20aims%20to%20predict%20not%20just%20career%20success%20or%20fashion%20choices%20but%20something%20far%20more%20profound%3A%20the%20very%20outcome%20of%20a%20person's%20life.%20It's%20like%20holding%20a%20mirror%20to%20the%20past%2C%20seeking%20to%20glimpse%20the%20future%20it%20reflects.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703131920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fj4lbd4g_artificial-intelligence_625x300_01_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fais-death-prediction-tool-claims-remarkable-accuracy-know-the-details-4713893%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Researchers%20have%20created%20an%20artificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%20chatbot%20that%20can%20predict%20when%20you%20will%20die%20with%2078%25%20accuracy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fais-death-prediction-tool-claims-remarkable-accuracy-know-the-details-4713893%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fais-death-prediction-tool-claims-remarkable-accuracy-know-the-details-47