%20of%20age%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fixed%20drug%20combination%20comprises%20chlorpheniramine%20maleate%20and%20phenylephrine%20-%20medication%20that%20is%20often%20used%20in%20syrups%20or%20tablets%20to%20treat%20common%20cold%20symptoms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Health%20Organization%20does%20not%20recommend%20the%20use%20of%20over-the-counter%20cough%20syrups%20or%20medicines%20for%20the%20treatment%20of%20coughs%20and%20cold%20symptoms%20in%20children%20younger%20than%20five%20years%20of%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20here%20have%20introduced%20mandatory%20testing%20for%20cough%20syrup%20exports%20since%20June%20and%20stepped%20up%20scrutiny%20of%20drugmakers.%20Drugmakers%20whose%20cough%20syrups%20were%20linked%20to%20child%20deaths%20have%20denied%20any%20wrong%20doing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703131680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2Fpkkjg5b_syrup-generic-unsplash_625x300_13_October_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-bans-anti-cold-drug-for-children-below-4-after-syrup-deaths-claim-4713932%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20drugs%20regulator%20in%20India%20has%20banned%20the%20use%20of%20an%20anti-cold%20drug%20combination%20in%20children%20aged%20below%20four%20and%20ordered%20that%20drugs%20should%20be%20labelled%20accordingly%2C%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20deaths%20of%20at%20least%20141%20children%20globally%20linked%20to%20cough%20syrups.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-bans-anti-cold-drug-for-children-below-4-after-syrup-deaths-claim-4713932%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-bans-anti-c