mount's%20CBS%20and%20WBD's%20CNN%20together%20would%20make%20a%20formidable%20news%20organization%2C%20and%20the%20companies'%20streaming%20services%20%E2%80%94%20Paramount%2B%20and%20Max%20%E2%80%94%20have%20complementary%20strengths.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20shares%20of%20both%20companies%20declined%20today%20amid%20news%20of%20the%20talks%2C%20Warner%20by%205.6%25%20and%20Paramount%20by%202%25%2C%20and%20other%20analysts%20threw%20cold%20water%20on%20a%20deal%20being%20a%20cure-all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsolidation%20won't%20fix%20legacy%20media's%20streaming%20woes%2C%20LightShed%20Partners%20argued%20in%20a%20December%2019%20note.%20They're%20too%20late%20and%20lack%20the%20talent%20and%20strategy%20to%20build%20scaled%20streamers%20while%20managing%20their%20linear%20TV%20declines%2C%20and%20layering%20on%20more%20linear%20TV%20assets%20to%20a%20WBD%20or%20Paramount%20%26quot%3Bfeels%20like%20a%20financial%20death%20sentence%2C%26quot%3B%20LightShed%20wrote.%20LightShed's%20Richard%20Greenfield%20doubled%20down%20on%20that%20argument%20Wednesday%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCNBCFastMoney%2Fstatus%2F1737611067637858539%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterview%20with%20CNBC%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20advocating%20for%20WBD%20to%20exit%20the%20streaming%20wars%20and%20focus%20on%20being%20a%20great%20%26quot%3Barms%20dealer%26quot%3B%20creating%20content%20for%20other%20buyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20true%20that%20WBD%20and%20Paramount%20could%20benefit%20from%20efficiencies%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20content%20creation%2C%20and%20Zaslav%2C%20who%20has%20talked%20up%20the%20value%20of%20live%20sports%2C%20could%20be%20looking%20at%20Paramount's%20sports%20rights%20as%20a%20way%20of%20boosting%20that%20part%20of%20WBD's%20business%2C%20Edward%20Jones%20analyst%20David%20Heger%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20investors%20may%20be%20gun%20shy%20given%20WBD's%20still-heavy%20debt%20load%20(of%20%2445%20billion)%2C%20the