a%20little%20more%20fit%20after%20his%20daughter%20was%20born%2C%20and%20was%20training%20for%20obstacle%20races%20before%20he%20ever%20walked%20into%20a%20powerlifting%20gym.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20decided%20didn't%20like%20the%20running%20but%20liked%20the%20weights%2C%26quot%3B%20Squires%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Squires%20was%20involved%20in%20dog%20rescue%2C%20and%20said%20the%20process%20prompted%20him%20to%20start%20cutting%20meat%20out%20of%20his%20diet%20for%20ethical%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20this%20cognitive%20dissonance%20about%20spending%20time%2C%20money%2C%20and%20energy%20helping%20these%20animals%20and%20eating%20other%20animals.%20It%20weighed%20on%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20a%20year%2C%20he%20gradually%20transitioned%20to%20a%20fully%20plant-based%20diet%2C%20which%20provides%20plenty%20of%20fuel%20for%20big%20lifts%3A%20Squires%20has%20since%20put%20up%20all-time%20personal%20bests%20of%20374%20pounds%20on%20the%20bench%20press%2C%20a%20611%20pound%20squat%2C%20and%20a%20666%20pound%20deadlift.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20his%20daily%20routine%20for%20moving%20big%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHis%20typical%20diet%20includes%20more%20than%20220%20grams%20of%20protein%20from%20plants%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20most%20vegan%20athletes%2C%20Squires%20is%20used%20to%20questions%20about%20how%20he%20gets%20enough%20food%2C%20and%20enough%20protein%2C%20to%20build%20muscle%20and%20strength%20on%20a%20plant-based%20diet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20typical%20day%20of%20eating%20for%20him%20includes%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBreakfast%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Oatmeal%2C%20vegan%20protein%20powder%2C%20and%20banana%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELunch%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20stereotypical%20bodybuilder-style%20meal%2C%20with%20a%20twist%20%E2%80%94%20broccoli%20and%20rice%2C%20but%20with%20vegan%20%26quot%3Bch