2090%20to%20120%20minutes%20each%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20move%20thousands%20of%20pounds%20in%20a%20workout%2C%20Squires%20said%20the%20key%20is%20rest%2C%20both%20between%20sets%20and%20between%20workouts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20taking%20500%20pounds%20off%20the%20rack%20and%20moving%20it%2C%20it%20takes%20a%20lot%20out%20of%20your%20body%2C%20so%20don't%20want%20to%20rush%20into%20your%20next%20set%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20rest%20day%20are%20key%20to%20allow%20the%20muscles%20to%20build%20back%20stronger%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fwarning-signs-exercising-too-much-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprevent%20overtraining%20which%20can%20stall%20progress%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20have%20the%20idea%20that%20you%20have%20to%20be%20in%20the%20gym%20every%20day.%20Half%20the%20work%20is%20the%20body%20recovery%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESquires%20said%20he%20spends%20time%20on%20a%20Peloton%20doing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Factive-recovery-strategies-reduce-muscle-soreness-boost-muscle-gains-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eactive%20recovery%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20periods%20of%20light%20movement%20that%20can%20improve%20blood%20flow%20to%20speed%20muscle%20healing%2C%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENear%20competition%2C%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2F3-training-tips-world-record-powerlifter-uses-move-heavy-weights-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraining%20cycle%3C%2Fa%3E%20eases%20up%20on%20volume%20so%20he's%20performing%20fewer%20reps%2C%20giving%20his%20muscles%20time%20to%20be%20in%20peak%20shape%20for%20the%20meet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESquires%20said%20that%20what%20he%20loves%20about%20powerlifting%20is%20the%20focus%20on%20performance%20instead%20of%20aesthetics%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20whole%20life%2C%20I'd%20sign%20up%20for%20a%20gym%20