0High-abrasion%20areas%20of%20the%20parka%20(like%20the%20sleeves)%20are%20reinforced%20with%20Cordura%20fabric%20for%20added%20durability.%20While%20I'm%20usually%20mindful%20about%20taking%20care%20of%20my%20garments%2C%20I%20appreciated%20the%20extra%20durability%20because%20of%20how%20expensive%20Canada%20Goose%20can%20be.%20The%20parka%20has%20reflective%20accents%2C%20which%20add%20visibility%20in%20low%20light%2C%20but%20also%20simply%20look%20cool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Brockton%20Parka%20is%20thoughtfully%20designed%20to%20keep%20you%20warm%2C%20but%20one%20of%20its%20best%20features%20helps%20you%20cool%20off%20when%20needed.%20The%20inside%20features%20interior%20backpack%20straps%2C%20so%20you%20can%20carry%20the%20jacket%20hands-free.%20I've%20found%20this%20to%20be%20a%20super%20useful%20feature%20on%20other%20Canada%20Goose%20jackets%20I've%20tested%20as%20it's%20kept%20me%20from%20overheating%20while%20in%20the%20subway%2C%20in%20the%20mall%2C%20or%20in%20between%20runs%20while%20snow%20tubing.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20worth%20pointing%20out%20that%20the%20sizing%20of%20Canada%20Goose's%20parkas%20tends%20to%20run%20a%20little%20bigger%20than%20a%20normal%20coat.%20I%20typically%20size%20up%20to%20a%20medium%20for%20an%20oversized%20fit%2C%20but%20going%20with%20my%20true%20size%2C%20small%2C%20gives%20me%20the%20perfect%20oversized%20fit%20I%20like.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20our%20full%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fcanada-goose-cold-room-review%5C%22%3ECanada%20Goose%20Cold%20Room%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMost%20stylish%3A%20The%20North%20Face%20HMLYN%20Down%20Parka%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20standing%20on%20the%20sidewalk%20wearing%20the%20The%20North%20Face%20HMLYN%20Down%20Parka.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65832c97cefc010bea25abf5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3