0oils%20are%20used%20for%20moisture%20and%20scent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20worried%20about%20an%20all-natural%20deodorant%20that%20doesn't%20deliver%20in%20the%20scent%20department%2C%20Dr.%20Squatch%20won't%20let%20you%20down.%20Some%20of%20my%20favorite%20scents%20are%20Wood%20Barrel%20Bourbon%2C%20Rainforest%20Rapids%2C%20and%20Fresh%20Fall%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20which%20last%20for%20hours%20on%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAside%20its%20distinctly%20masculine%20scents%2C%20Dr.%20Squatch's%20products%20are%20formulated%20specifically%20for%20men%20by%20including%20additional%20ingredients%20that%20can%20be%20potentially%20beneficial%20to%20men's%20health%2C%20such%20as%20saw%20palmetto%2C%20ginseng%2C%20and%20valerian.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20natural%20with%20baking%20soda%3A%20American%20Provenance%3Cp%3EFounded%20by%20Kyle%20LaFond%2C%20a%20former%20middle%20school%20science%20teacher%2C%20American%20Provenance%20is%20a%20natural%20care%20essentials%20brand.%20All%20of%20the%20deodorants%20are%20hand-mixed%2C%20hand-poured%2C%20and%20made%20in%20small%20batches%20here%20in%20the%20USA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20brand%20uses%20what%20it%20calls%20%26quot%3Bbetter-for-you%20ingredients%26quot%3B%20in%20its%20products.%20The%20deodorant%20uses%20coconut%20oil%20for%20its%20antibacterial%20properties%2C%20baking%20soda%20to%20deodorize%2C%20arrowroot%20to%20absorb%20sweat%20and%20bodily%20oils%2C%20and%20beeswax%20and%20shea%20butter%20to%20hydrate%20and%20soothe%20the%20skin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20few%20scents%20I've%20used%2C%20none%20of%20them%20smell%20particularly%20masculine%20or%20feminine%2C%20so%20it's%20one%20of%20the%20best%20deodorant%20choices%20if%20you're%20looking%20for%20a%20unisex%20deodorant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20sensitive%20skin%3A%20Bevel%3Cp%3EBevel%20is%20a%20Black-owned%20grooming%20brand%20that%20makes%20affordable%20essentials%20for%20people%20of%20color.%20With%20everything%20from%20safety%20razors%20that%20pre