this%20might%20not%20be%20the%20one%20for%20you.%20However%2C%20each%20name%20clearly%20describes%20the%20scent%20profile%2C%20so%20it's%20easy%20to%20choose%20one%20you'll%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20moisturizing%3A%20Dove%20Men%2BCare%3Cp%3EDeodorant%20is%20used%20to%20keep%20body%20odor%20under%20control%2C%20but%20harsh%20ingredients%20can%20often%20have%20a%20negative%20effect%20on%20your%20underarm%20skin.%20If%20you're%20dealing%20with%20dry%2C%20peeling%2C%20or%20itchy%20skin%20on%20your%20underarms%2C%20there's%20a%20good%20chance%20that%20your%20skin%20doesn't%20agree%20with%20your%20current%20deodorant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dove.com%2Fus%2Fen%2Fmen-care%2Fdeodorant.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDove%20Men%2BCare%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20developed%20to%20meet%20the%20needs%20of%20men%2C%20while%20nourishing%20skin.%20Of%20the%20many%20deodorant%20choices%20from%20Dove%20Men%2BCare%2C%20I%20most%20recommend%20the%20Extra%20Fresh%20Deodorant%20Stick.%20This%20formula%20is%20aluminum-free%20and%20is%20made%20with%20%C2%BC%20moisturizing%20cream%2C%20so%20it%20won't%20irritate%20your%20skin.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20said%20to%20have%2072-hour%20odor%20protection%2C%20and%20while%20I've%20never%20gone%20that%20long%20without%20showering%20and%20re-applying%20deodorant%2C%20it%20does%20an%20excellent%20job%20at%20lasting%20all%20day.%20The%20%26quot%3Bextra%20fresh%26quot%3B%20scent%20is%20a%20blend%20of%20bergamot%2C%20lavender%2C%20and%20sandalwood%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20which%20suppress%20odor%20and%20keep%20you%20smelling%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20high-end%3A%20Jack%20Black%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%202000%2C%20when%20the%20grooming%20and%20beauty%20industry%20was%20primarily%20saturated%20with%20products%20for%20women%2C%20Jack%20Black%20was%20one%20of%20earliest%20brands%20to%20create%20high-quality%20grooming%20essentials%20using%20natural%20ingredients%20for%20men.%20While%20the%20market%20has%20plenty%20of%20natural%20or%20clean%20brands%20for%20men%2C%20Jack%20Black%20is%20still%20one%20of%20the%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJack%20Black's%20Pit%20Boss%20antiperspirant%20is%20free%20of%20parabens%20and%20sulfates%20and%20uses%20natural%20ingredients%20like%20vitamin%20E%2C%20aloe%20leaf%20juice%2C%20castor%20oil%2C%20and%20sunflower%20seed%20oil%20to%20protect%20and%20moisturize%20the%20skin.%20As%20an%20antiperspirant%2C%20it%20uses%20aluminum%20to%20reduce%20underarm%20wetness%20and%20control%20sweat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20won't%20get%20to%20choose%20between%20a%20variety%20of%20scents%20with%20Jack%20Black%20Pit%20Boss%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20mind%20because%20it%20has%20one%20of%20the%20freshest%20scents%20I've%20tried%20and%20lasts%20all%20day%20long.%20It's%20one%20of%20the%20priciest%20products%20on%20this%20lists%2C%20but%20with%20its%20effectiveness%20and%20attractive%20scent%2C%20it's%20still%20worth%20trying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20aluminum-free%3A%20Bravo%20Sierra%3Cp%3EDrawing%20inspiration%20from%20military%20culture%2C%20Bravo%20Sierra%20is%20a%20utilitarian-based%20unisex%20grooming%20company.%20The%20brand's%20popular%20four-in-one%20face%20cleanser%2C%20body%20wash%2C%20shampoo%2C%20and%20shave%20gel%20effectively%20eliminates%20the%20need%20for%20a%20bunch%20of%20different%20products%2C%20but%20if%20there's%20one%20more%20essential%20you%20need%20from%20them%2C%20it's%20the%20deodorant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20using%20aluminum%20or%20baking%20soda%20to%20prevent%20sweat%2C%20Bravo%20Sierra's%20natural%20formula%20uses%20a%20sweat-absorptive%20power%20extracted%20from%20cassava%20root%2C%20a%20plant%20native%20to%20Brazil.%20In%20comparison%20to%20some%20other%20natural%20deodorants%20I've%20tested%2C%20Bravo%20Sierra%20adequately%20lived%20up%20to%20my%20daily%20needs.%20It%20didn't%20wear%20off%20easily%20or%20need%20to%20be%20reapplied%20midday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp