Bills%20were%20first%20taken%20up%20for%20passage%20and%20consideration%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20hours%20after%2049%20opposition%20MPs%20were%20suspended%20from%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20following%20protests%20in%20the%20house%20demanding%20a%20statement%20from%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20on%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fparliament-security-breach-anniversary-slogan-dictatorship%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esecurity%20breach%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20parliament%20last%20week.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20as%20the%20debate%20continued%20in%20the%20afternoon%2C%20it%20was%20paused%20for%20a%20few%20minutes%20as%20parliamentary%20affairs%20minister%20Pralhad%20Joshi%20came%20in%20to%20announce%20the%20suspension%20of%20two%20more%20opposition%20MPs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20December%2014%2C%20a%20total%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2F141-here-are-all-the-mps-suspended-from-parliament-this-winter-session%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E143%20opposition%20MPs%20have%20been%20suspended%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20total%20of%2035%20MPs%20participated%20in%20the%20debate%20over%20the%20three%20new%20criminal%20Bills%20over%20the%20course%20of%20the%20two%20days%20(Tuesday%20and%20Wednesday).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20debate%20saw%20the%20participation%20of%20MPs%20from%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20and%20parliamentarians%20from%20parties%20friendly%20to%20it%20like%20the%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%2C%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20and%20the%20YSR%20Congress%20Party%2C%20who%20also%20supported%20the%20legislation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnly%20MPs%20from%20the%20All%20India%20Majlis-e-Ittehadul%20Muslimeen%20(AIMIM)%20and%20the%20Shiromani%20Akali%20Dal%20(SAD)%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20Bills%