y%20(BJP)%20MP%20from%20Karnataka.%20The%20two%20of%20them%20who%20entered%20the%20parliament%20had%20hidden%20the%20spray%20bottle%20used%20in%20the%20break%20inside%20their%20shoes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20breach%20occurred%20on%20the%2021st%20anniversary%20of%20the%202001%20terror%20attack%20on%20the%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAround%20the%20same%20time%2C%20a%20man%20and%20a%20woman%20%E2%80%93%20Amol%20Shinde%20and%20Neelam%20Azad%E2%80%93%20sprayed%20coloured%20gas%20from%20canisters%20while%20also%20shouting%20slogans%20like%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9Ctana%20shahi%20nahi%20chalegi%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20outside%20the%20parliament%20premises.%20Azad%20is%20from%20Haryana%E2%80%99s%20Jind%20and%20has%20many%20degrees%20to%20her%20credit%2C%20M.A%2C%20M.Ed%2C%20M.Phil%20and%20has%20also%20cleared%20the%20National%20Eligibility%20Test.%20Yet%2C%20she%20could%20not%20get%20any%20job.%20Slogans%20shouted%20by%20them%20were%20against%20dictatorship%2C%20for%20protection%20of%20the%20constitution%20and%20rising%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20unemployment.%20They%20also%20shouted%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Bharat%20Mata%20Ki%20Jai%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EVande%20Mataram%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20individuals%20were%20part%20of%20a%20social%20media%20group%2C%20%E2%80%98Bhagat%20Singh%20Fans%20Club%E2%80%99%2C%20where%20they%20came%20in%20contact%20with%20each%20other.%20Their%20inspiration%20for%20these%20actions%20stemmed%20from%20socialist%20revolutionary%20Bhagat%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20similar%20actions%20in%20the%20central%20assembly%20hall%20in%201929.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EBhagat%20Singh%20with%20his%20friend%20Batukeshwar%20Dutt%20had%20thrown%20a%20bomb%20from%20the%20visitors%E2%80%99%20gallery%20while%20making%20sure%20that%20nobody%20was%20hurt.%20They%20also%20threw%20leaflets%20in%20the%20assembly%20against%20British%20colonial%20rule.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Ffreedom-fighter-batukeshwar-dutt-birth-anniversary%5C%22%3EBatukeshwar%20Dutt%3A%20A%20Working%20Class%20Revolutionary%E2%80%99s%20Life%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20four%20people%20have%20been%20booked%20under%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20(UAPA)%2C%20this%20incident%20is%20the%20most%20powerful%20attempt%20to%20bring%20the%20issue%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Findia-narendra-modi-jobs-unemployment%5C%22%3Erising%20unemployment%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20national%20attention.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20recall%2C%20Bhagat%20Singh%20and%20his%20comrades%20had%20resorted%20to%20this%20method%20as%20they%20knew%20that%20their%20voice%20would%20not%20be%20carried%20by%20the%20media.%20There%20is%20an%20uncanny%20similarity%20to%20the%20current%20situation%20where%20the%20%E2%80%98mainstream%E2%80%99%20media%2C%20appropriately%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newslaundry.com%2F2023%2F07%2F25%2Fravish-kumar-writes-big-money-is-no-guarantee-of-a-healthy-accountable-and-free-media%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Godi%20media%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20totally%20apathetic%20to%20the%20concerns%20of%20the%20common%20people.%20The%20problems%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dxi54qNKYDM0%5C%22%3Erising%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsclick.in%2Fbihar-caste-survey-eye-opener-indias-poverty-spread%5C%22%3Epoverty%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newslaundry.com%2F2022%2F06%2F25%2Ftv-newsance-176-the-data-on-job-debates-studio-veers-dont-want-you-to-know%5C%22%3Eunemployment%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20not%20been%20its%20concern%20at%20all.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20Modi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fjobs-justice-and-smart-cities-the-promises-bjp-made-in-its-2014-manifesto%5C%22%3