%20Singh.%20Credit%3A%20Traditional%20image%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20attributed%20the%20attack%20to%20rising%20unemployment%20and%20inflation%20while%20the%20home%20minister%20has%20not%20made%20any%20statement%20in%20parliament%2C%20despite%20the%20opposition%20demanding%20it.%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%2C%20rather%20than%20seeing%20the%20obvious%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-parliament-security-breach-probe-needed-not-debate-pms-1st-remarks-on-parliament-security-breach-4689780%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20this%20act%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cserious%20breach%E2%80%9D%20and%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20find%20the%20elements%20behind%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20true%20that%20the%20chink%20in%20the%20armour%20of%20the%20security%20system%20in%20parliament%20has%20been%20exposed%3B%20it%E2%80%99s%20vulnerable%20to%20even%20minor%20attempts%20like%20that%20of%20these%20young%20individuals.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20it%20has%20highlighted%20the%20need%20to%20address%20the%20issue%20of%20unemployment%20rather%20than%20seeing%20it%20as%20some%20sort%20of%20a%20conspiracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20clear%20these%20individuals%20are%20not%20part%20of%20any%20terror%20group.%20Mercifully%2C%20none%20of%20the%20involved%20youth%20is%20a%20Muslim%2C%20neither%20do%20they%20belong%20to%20any%20terror-related%20organisation.%20The%20latter%20would%20have%20given%20an%20unfortunate%20boost%20to%20the%20efforts%20of%20those%20out%20to%20intensify%20Islamophobia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20incident%20should%20serve%20as%20a%20reminder%20that%20it%20is%20not%20enough%20to%20just%20pay%20lip%20service%20to%20Bhagat%20Singh.%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20concern%20for%20the%20deprived%20sections%20of%20society%20needs%20to%20be%20highlighted.%20Let%20us%20remember%20that%20mass%20movements%20were%20central%20to%20his%20ideology.%20The%20path%20of%20violence%20was%20abandoned%20by%20him.%20He%2