0href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uscirf.gov%2Freligious-prisoners-conscience%2Fforb-victims-database%2Fmeeran-haider%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHaider%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20PhD%20research%20scholar%20at%20Jamia%20Millia%20Islamia%20and%20a%20political%20activist%2C%20filed%20his%20bail%20plea%20in%20May%202022.%20Since%20then%2C%20his%20case%20has%20been%20listed%2060%20times.%20However%2C%20arguments%20took%20place%20only%20on%20four%20dates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20proceedings%20%E2%80%93%20such%20as%20issuance%20of%20notice%2C%20calling%20for%20counter%20affidavits%20or%20other%20procedural%20work%20%E2%80%93%20happened%20on%20five%20other%20dates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%2060%20days%20his%20case%20was%20listed%2C%20there%20were%20a%20total%20of%20nine%20productive%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwenty%20times%2C%20the%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20orders%20noted%20that%20the%20special%20bench%20%E2%80%9Cdid%20not%20assemble%E2%80%9D%2C%20seven%20times%20due%20to%20one%20judge%20on%20the%20bench%20being%20on%20leave%20or%20unavailable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20Arjun%20Dewan%2C%20counsel%20for%20one%20of%20the%20other%20accused%2C%20Athar%2C%20told%C2%A0%3Cem%3EArticle%2014%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20special%20bench%20may%20have%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20assemble.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Mridul%20and%20Justice%20Bhatnagar%20were%20both%20heading%20separate%20benches%20and%20had%20to%20especially%20sit%20together%20to%20form%20this%20special%20bench.%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6%20which%20could%20have%20been%20a%20hassle%20sometimes%20because%20each%20had%20their%20own%20roster%20and%20heavy%20workload%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dewan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CA%20regular%20bench%20sits%20every%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20continued%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwhile%20a%20special%20bench%20sits%20once%20a%20week%20usually.%20So%20a%20regular%20bench%20could%20have%20heard%20the%20cases%20more%20expeditiously.%20Hence%20you%20see%20so%20many%20times%20the%20co