er.%20But%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20use%20of%20talent%20if%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20work%20on%20it.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%226%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrust%20your%20instincts%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20day%20the%20results%20came%20out%20is%20etched%20in%20Kalpit%E2%80%99s%20memory.%20But%20he%20shares%20an%20anecdote%20of%20a%20time%20much%20before%20the%20D-Day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20checking%20around%20with%20my%20friends%20and%20coaching%20classes%20that%20had%20released%20their%20answer%20keys.%20There%20was%20this%20one%20question%20in%20particular%20that%20was%20tricky.%20Everyone%20was%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327615%2Fengineer-animates-ncert-syllabus-turns-govt-schools-into-digital-classrooms-muskaan-dreams%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20opinion%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20I%20had%20attempted%20it%20by%20an%20incorrect%20method.%20But%20I%20was%20sure%20I%20was%20right.%20I%20remember%20my%20friends%20saying%20to%20me%2C%20%E2%80%98No%20one%20will%20think%20of%20such%20a%20strange%20way%20of%20solving%20this%E2%80%99.%20When%20the%20results%20were%20announced%2C%20needless%20to%20say%2C%20my%20method%20was%20the%20right%20one.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTrust%20your%20gut%20feeling%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FU6koEEdIpLI%3Fsi%3DcXgSrDpUK_e8_ceD%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20JEE%20Mains%20exam%2C%20Kalpit%20started%20a%20Facebook%20page%20where%20he%20would%20advise%20students%20on%20preparing%20for%20the%20exam%2C%20books%20to%20refer%20to%2C%20etc.%20In%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20he%20had%20a%20Quora%20account%20where%20he%20would%20answer%20stud